      <title>美元坚挺，日元下滑，因美联储削减押注而崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-yen-skids-fed-cut-wagers-crumble-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，美国通胀数据高于预期，打压了人们对美联储将于 6 月开始降息周期的预期，美元周四坚挺，而日元则徘徊在 1990 年中期的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-yen-skids-fed-cut-wagers-crumble-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 01:27:57 GMT</pubDate>
